casebody.data:
Gage Bernard Walldren, a minor, by Delema Meyer, his aunt and next friend, defendant in error, v. Joseph G. Weber, plaintiff in error.

First District.

Gen. No. 35,312.Heard in the second division of this court for the first district at the October term, 1931.Opinion filed February 23, 1932.Ernest Kentwortz, for plaintiff in error. No appearance for defendant in error. Mr. Presiding Justice Gridley

delivered the opinion of the court.
